PART XII — SECTION 1: TECH STACK (EXACT VERSIONS, ZERO DEVIATION)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

RUNTIME:         Node.js 22.11.0 EXACT
PACKAGE MANAGER: pnpm 9.12.3 EXACT (never npm, never yarn)
                 pnpm-workspace.yaml MUST exist at monorepo root.
LANGUAGE:        TypeScript 5.7.x EXACT
                 strict: true, noImplicitAny: true,
                 strictNullChecks: true — zero 'any' types permitted.
FRONTEND:        React 19 + Vite 7
BUILD TOOLING:   vite-plugin-node-polyfills (REQUIRED for browser-side
                 crypto/buffer — AES and Vibrant.js)
STYLING:         Tailwind CSS 4 + CSS custom properties
                 Zero inline styles. Zero hardcoded hex values in TSX.
ANIMATION:       Framer Motion 11
3D ENGINE:       React Three Fiber + @react-three/drei + Three.js r128
                 FORBIDDEN: CapsuleGeometry (not in r128)
                 REQUIRED: OrbitControls via @react-three/drei only
AUDIO:           Web Audio API (native browser — no external library)
COLOR EXTRACT:   Vibrant.js
DRAG AND DROP:   @dnd-kit/sortable
API SERVER:      Express 5 (port 8080)
DATABASE:        PostgreSQL 16 + Drizzle ORM
QUEUE + CACHE:   Redis 7.2 Alpine (BullMQ integration)
STORAGE:         AWS S3 SDK v3
ENCRYPTION:      Node.js crypto (AES-256-GCM)
AUTH:            bcrypt + JWT (httpOnly cookies, 24h access / 30d refresh)
SERVER BUILD:    esbuild (CJS bundle)
BLUR HASH:       blurhash

VERSION LOCK ENFORCEMENT:
  ALL package versions MUST be pinned exactly.
  Caret (^), tilde (~), latest, beta, rc, and canary are forbidden in
  any package.json across the entire monorepo.

PORTS:
  Frontend dev: 18956
  API server:   8080
  PostgreSQL:   5432
  Redis:        6379

