  - Every system module MUST rely on a local Mock Controller before live
    gateway activation.
  - All default test payloads MUST use the full 6-language schema:
    { en, es, fr, zh, ja, ko }.
  - Local fallback data MUST simulate real-world streaming latency (< 120ms)
    to benchmark frontend rendering under stress.

DYNAMIC CMS API INJECTION LAW:
  - Environment variable redeployments for API keys are forbidden.
