────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
TAB 2 — MEDIA PIPELINE
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  Drop zone: 100% width, 200px height, animated dashed border.
    Accept: .mp3, .wav, YouTube URLs.
    Drag-over: border -> accent-color, scale 1.02.

  Pipeline progress: animated stage indicators + estimated time.
    Stages map to PipelineStatus type.

  Generated art preview:
    Before/after: original vs AI-generated art.
    Theme filter preview: 3 panels (ONYX / CYBER / MINIMAL).
