  Approval gate:
    "Approve & Publish" with confirmation modal -> POST /api/pipeline/approve/:jobId

  Playlist manager:
    @dnd-kit drag handles. Cover thumbnail, title, genre badge, duration.
    is_live toggle per track. Delete with confirmation.

  Real-time telemetry console:
    SSE from /api/pipeline/status/:jobId.
    Auto-scrolling log: INFO (white), WARN (amber), ERROR (red), SUCCESS (green).
    Each log entry: timestamp + stage + message.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
TAB 3 — UNIVERSAL INJECTION PANEL (API GATEKEEPER HUB)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  Security: all inputs type="password", never stored in localStorage.
  Encryption: AES-256-GCM before database storage.
  Storage: api_keys table (encrypted_value + iv + auth_tag).

  Panel-managed keys (live injection via UI):
    AI_IMAGE_GENERATION_KEY — OpenAI DALL-E 3
    LLM_NARRATIVE_API_KEY   — OpenAI GPT-4o
    YOUTUBE_API_DATA_V3     — YouTube Data API v3

  Environment-only keys (MUST be in .env — not injectable via UI):
    ENCRYPTION_MASTER_KEY   — 32-byte hex string, .env ONLY
    SMTP_SERVER             — .env ONLY
    SMTP_PORT               — .env ONLY (default: 587)
    SMTP_USER               — .env ONLY
    SMTP_PASSWORD           — .env ONLY
    DATABASE_URL            — .env ONLY
    REDIS_URL               — .env ONLY
    JWT_SECRET              — .env ONLY
    AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID       — .env ONLY
    AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY   — .env ONLY
    AWS_REGION              — .env ONLY
    AWS_S3_BUCKET_NAME      — .env ONLY

  Each panel-managed field:
    - Input with show/hide toggle
    - "Test Connection" -> POST /api/keys/test
    - Status: Connected / Not configured / Error + timestamp

  Without AI keys: AI features show "Configure API Keys in Admin Panel".
  With AI keys: full autonomous pipeline activates instantly.

