       - Noto Sans SC (400, 500)
       - Noto Sans KR (400, 500)
  7. Google Fonts stylesheet link with font-display=swap
  8. favicon reference: /assets/favicon.ico
  9. OG meta tags for social sharing
  10. <meta name="theme-color" content="#080808">
  11. <div id="root"></div> — root React mount point
  12. <script type="module" src="/src/main.tsx"></script>
  13. ZERO inline styles in index.html
  14. ZERO hardcoded colors in index.html
  15. preconnect links to fonts.googleapis.com and fonts.gstatic.com
  16. dns-prefetch for CDN origins
  17. Safe area meta for iOS:
      <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0,
      viewport-fit=cover">
  18. Apple touch icon reference
  19. Zero layout-shift-inducing resources loaded synchronously
  20. All script tags deferred or module type

