  - JWT middleware verifying httpOnly cookie
  - Login: bcrypt.compare -> access JWT (24h) + refresh JWT (30d)
  - Logout: clear both cookies
  - Refresh: validate refresh JWT -> issue new access JWT
  - Failed attempts counter with 5-attempt lockout (15 minutes)
  - All admin routes (except GET /api/identity and GET /api/tracks)
    MUST require valid JWT middleware

