  - canvas.addEventListener('webglcontextrestored', handler)
  - On restore: re-initialize all geometries, re-upload textures,
    resume requestAnimationFrame
  - Hook: useWebGLContextGuard(rendererRef) attaches/detaches on mount/unmount

