PROMPT 37 [Architectural Lenis Smooth Scroll Engine]:
  Complete setup at:
    artifacts/ace-2026/src/hooks/useSmoothScroll.ts
  MUST include:
  - Integration of @studio-freight/lenis for global scroll hijacking.
  - Configuration Matrix:
      duration: 1.2
      easing: (t) => Math.min(1, 1.001 - Math.pow(2, -10 * t))
      direction: 'vertical'
      smooth: true
      smoothTouch: false
  - requestAnimationFrame MUST be synchronized explicitly with Framer
    Motion and Three.js useFrame.
  - Native browser scroll behavior MUST be explicitly disabled via CSS
    (overflow: hidden on body).
  - WebGL camera Y-axis translation MUST sync seamlessly with Lenis
    scroll output.
  - Cleanup: lenis.destroy() on unmount to prevent memory leaks.

