PROMPT 42 [Zero-Downtime GitHub Actions CI/CD Manifest]:
  Complete workflow at .github/workflows/deploy.yml. MUST include:
  - Trigger: push to main
  - Step 1: pnpm install --frozen-lockfile
  - Step 2: pnpm run typecheck (fail on any TypeScript error)
  - Step 3: pnpm run lint (fail on any ESLint error)
  - Step 4: pnpm run test (fail on any test failure)
  - Step 5: pnpm run build (Vite frontend + esbuild API)
  - Step 6: Wait for PostgreSQL healthy (pg_isready loop, max 30s)
  - Step 7: pnpm run db:migrate (ONLY after PostgreSQL verified)
  - Step 8: Deploy frontend to CDN, API to server
  - Step 9: Nginx reload (ONLY after migrations complete)
  - Step 10: GET /api/health -> 200 required
  - On failure: rollback deployment, alert via configured channel
  - Zero downtime: new container starts before old container stops

