Format: OpenAPI 3.0
This file is the source of truth for all API contracts.

Required sections:
  openapi: "3.0.0"
  info:
    title: ACE-2026 API
    version: "1.0.0"
  servers:
    - url: http://localhost:8080 (development)
    - url: https://api.ace-2026.com (production)
